field.groups0.name: Default
field.groups0.parameters0.name: base_global_planner
field.groups0.parameters0.description: The name of the plugin for the global planner to use with move_base.
field.groups0.parameters1.name: base_local_planner
field.groups0.parameters1.description: The name of the plugin for the local planner to use with move_base.
field.groups0.parameters2.name: planner_frequency
field.groups0.parameters2.description: The rate in Hz at which to run the planning loop.
field.groups0.parameters3.name: controller_frequency
field.groups0.parameters3.description: The rate in Hz at which to run the control loop and send velocity commands to the base.
field.groups0.parameters4.name: planner_patience
field.groups0.parameters4.description: How long the planner will wait in seconds in an attempt to find a valid plan before space-clearing operations are performed.
field.groups0.parameters5.name: controller_patience
field.groups0.parameters5.description: How long the controller will wait in seconds without receiving a valid control before space-clearing operations are performed.
field.groups0.parameters6.name: conservative_reset_dist
field.groups0.parameters6.description: The distance away from the robot in meters at which obstacles will be cleared from the costmap when attempting to clear space in the map.
field.groups0.parameters7.name: recovery_behavior_enabled
field.groups0.parameters7.description: Whether or not to enable the move_base recovery behaviors to attempt to clear out space.
field.groups0.parameters8.name: clearing_rotation_allowed
field.groups0.parameters8.description: Determines whether or not the robot will attempt an in-place rotation when attempting to clear out space.
field.groups0.parameters9.name: shutdown_costmaps
field.groups0.parameters9.description: Determines whether or not to shutdown the costmaps of the node when move_base is in an inactive state
field.groups0.parameters10.name: oscillation_timeout
field.groups0.parameters10.description: How long in seconds to allow for oscillation before executing recovery behaviors.
field.groups0.parameters11.name: oscillation_distance
field.groups0.parameters11.description: How far in meters the robot must move to be considered not to be oscillating.
field.groups0.parameters12.name: restore_defaults
